reviews.review_msg: Great professor, and interesting/challenging material. She will push you to reconsider your worldview, and can be pretty theoretical. Is very willing to help anyone who reaches out. Fair.
I enjoyed her class  and she the best!
I enjoyed the professor and the class (note, assignments are marked by a tutor marker). Highly recommend.
She's confusing. It is apparent she is a very bright woman, but, this is not transferred to teaching. It was supposed to be a writing class, but we are doing oral presentations. Bizarre.

Assignments- repetitive/boring, instead of giving constructive feedback her critiques are condescending/discouraging.I have 3.75 GPA and never received higher than a B from her. Current events at beginning of class are informative but seems as though she does not like to lecture and leaves the work to students. Class is purely on theory alone
